[07:06.66]	How to get clear of all the debts I owe.
[07:09.27]ANTONIO	I pray you, good Bassanio, let me know it;
[07:11.88]	And if it stand, as you yourself still do,
[07:14.55]	Within the eye of honour, be assured,
[07:16.94]	My purse, my person, my extremest means,
[07:19.44]	Lie all unlock'd to your occasions.
[07:21.76]BASSANIO	In my school-days, when I had lost one shaft,
